Re: "Freely" translated
by AJBryant » Wed 06.29.2011 10:26 am furrykef wrote:For instance, I love the Pioneer/Geneon dub of Lupin III even though it takes massive liberties with it -- obviously, there were no jokes about Shaq or eBay in the 70s. But it's funny, and that's the important thing.See, to me, that's inexcusable. Yeah, it may be funny, but that's actually changing the content. That's not reframing the joke. That's reWRITING the joke. I would be sending them hate letters.
